Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アルセス・タイタニア伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他找出来杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必特地叮嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索正在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就静候喜讯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有脸说！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁被他耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是谁让他侵入宅邸的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能之辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1127,923)\fad(500,500)}贝鲁提耶大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1127,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ベルティエ大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不如转移到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那种地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯伯被方修利盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻求孤的庇护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}渚士朗·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣认为没有理由拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}无地藩王 亚术曼·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}無地藩王 アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸卿可有异议？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚瑟斯那家伙自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若他不是我的弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若看到兄长弃弟弟于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要迎接亚瑟斯伯 还有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎物出巢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定不会放过这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1319,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1319,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫亚瑟斯伯一职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给臣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给身为兄长的哲力胥才合情合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲情会使人失去冷静的判断力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫感情用事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚士朗卿怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣认为伊德里斯卿更为适任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我单船出行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客船货船无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量避人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护卫舰队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带这么多累赘 想搞游行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利马上就会发现你 发起攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护我不是你的任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请您来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 伊德里斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若也算泰坦尼亚的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己想办法自保
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少自己来和我的舰队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无能之辈 休想自诩为泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 你是个虚有其表的人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准侮辱我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里都能去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 伊德里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1125,923)\fad(500,500)}李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1125,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ドクター・リー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯伯有所行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像想逃往天城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(755,923)\fad(500,500)}米兰达·卡西米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(755,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(687,923)\fad(500,500)}亚朗·麦佛迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(687,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アラン・マフディー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 杀了他就等于和整个泰坦尼亚为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵害死了莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要杀死伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士害怕和泰坦尼亚战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的研究课题是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「泰坦尼亚的盛衰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 我必须亲眼目睹泰坦尼亚的灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我会助提督一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我唯一的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四艘战舰从艾曼塔分别出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵在哪艘船上？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逐一击破吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一来 被干掉的会是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有舰队从天城出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(717,923)\fad(500,500)}路易·艾德蒙·巴杰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(717,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ルイ・エドモン・パジェス
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥官好像是伊德里斯·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四公爵之一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目标恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伯爵想必费了一番脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}战舰极光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}戦艦オーロラ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯舰队旗舰 火鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス艦隊旗艦 ファイアー・バード
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四艘战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每艘方向都各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他不要带护卫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然开出四艘战舰来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是堕落至极
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方舰队如何行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要随他耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天城出来的舰队动作出奇的慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方确实在邀请我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像还有别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚恐怕想让亚瑟斯伯去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯伯人格有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上层人物是想借此除去累赘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从放着兄长哲力胥不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而派伊德里斯迎接也能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵人缘也真差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意放任亚瑟斯被我们杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯再替他报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一举两得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是泰坦尼亚的惯用伎俩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回来吧 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩儿也想见母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}泰莉莎·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テリーザ・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不让我看看你？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你有精神的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是对你担心得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩儿很快就到天城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您暂时忍耐 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不去接他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是藩王殿下的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么借口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不担心弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁提耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还看不到伊德里斯卿的舰队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说已经离开天城了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他磨蹭什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被伯爵跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于 哪艘船是真货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要静观其变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方自然会露出马脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我也有些等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他的鼻子够好用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能由我们这边出手帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦知道亚瑟斯的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他马上就会发动袭击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时就是他的末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功之时请务必…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的舰队赶到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到伯爵阁下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这家伙没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向伊德里斯的舰队发信号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是泰坦尼亚贵族专用的通信编码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近防御 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封闭隔断墙 战斗准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的舰队也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你负责指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方发现敌舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离1200
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡航舰 总数15
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,径直向本舰冲来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为宇宙尘埃的会是方修利一行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敌人可不只一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区海贼 不管怎么聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下所搭乘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是泰坦尼亚引以为豪的战舰极光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯阁下也很快就会赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的指挥权能交给在下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把方修利杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦伦科夫 先攻击引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 敌舰引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,923)\fad(500,500)}米哈伊尔·瓦伦科夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミハエル・ワレンコフ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一机关室 严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法维持战速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全部炮火击中到敌舰头上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一举击溃他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰队 向两翼展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 会被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火 开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我的舰队攻击侧翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 右舷推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷推进器 受损
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我们动弹不得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁提耶 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度 对极光来说无关痛痒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁提耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击后方敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利肯定就在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中要把腹部暴露给敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方不知道什么叫战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侧面完全暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李舰队 左右夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主推进器 停止运转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 第三 第四 第六炮塔严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯舰队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯舰队没有任何动作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿真会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接伊德里斯阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来极光受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可能被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候只要替他们报仇就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬可悲的羔羊们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方一开始就有这个打算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 亚瑟斯阁下他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他 指挥官是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火 狠狠地打！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船怎么能被他们击沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手干掉方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让伊德里斯卿认同我的实力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会输吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一击由我亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标 战舰极光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极光 被击沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利舰的识别信号是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敌方的欺瞒信号妨碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知哪个是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法分辨方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时时都要考虑退路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星艾曼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星エーメンタール
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应当是开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此仇不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将方修利视为泰坦尼亚的公敌！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔真不会照顾花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像对待女生一样温柔就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 连这个都不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永远看着这种景象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿和哲力胥卿都视方修利为眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠他一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚要还的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方修利来说 宇宙越来越小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻 泰坦尼亚荣华依旧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数人还无法想象它会有终结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公主在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉亚瑟斯的死离我如此遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的周围也发生了异变
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(694,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}卢塔西的动乱


